The `contains` positional operator has the following syntax:

```json
{
  "$search": {
    "span": {
      "contains": {
        "spanToReturn": "inner"|"outer",
        "little": { <positional-or-term-operator-specification> },
        "big": { <positional-or-term-operator-specification> }
      }
    }
  }
}
```
